    "text": "Chess is a two-player strategy board game. 64 squares, 32 pieces per side. Goal: checkmate (king under attack with no escape). Pieces: pawn (1pt), knight/bishop (3), rook (5), queen (9). Three phases: opening (develop pieces, control center), middlegame (attack/defend), endgame (few pieces, promote pawns).",
